sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Start as start_server.py
    participant Main as main.py
    participant T1 as startup-pipelines thread
    participant T2 as rss-scrape thread
    participant T3 as news-prefetch thread
    participant Sched as APScheduler
    participant Orch as CrewAIOrchestrator
    participant DB as SQLite

    Start->>Main: uvicorn.run main:app
    Main->>DB: create_all tables

    Main->>T1: start daemon thread
    Main->>Sched: start_scheduler if enabled
    Main->>T2: RSS scrape thread
    Main->>T3: news prefetch thread

    par Startup pipeline
        T1->>Orch: run_monitor customer 71
        Orch->>DB: full pipeline run
        T1->>Main: update startup_pipeline_status
    and RSS warm
        T2->>T2: scrape_rss_feeds
        T2->>T2: article_cache refresh
    and News warm
        T3->>T3: get_headlines cache
    end
